WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:06.945
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me today. Well, I have some good news to tell y'all.

00:00:06.946 --> 00:00:14.496
In our live prayer session yesterday and the one before, I've done three videos over the last couple of days.

00:00:14.497 --> 00:00:35.425
And over the course of the time, Braden told me, he said, "We've had on this channel alone, 1,218 salvations."I was just like, "Wow."The Lord said He was bringing a stronger anointing for the unsaved to bring in the lost.

00:00:35.426 --> 00:00:41.017
And He told us we're going to start fishing with nets now. You know, it's happening. It's exciting.

00:00:41.017 --> 00:00:49.346
I just go, "Lord, this is too cool."Look at what this YouTube channel is doing, all for the glory of God.

00:00:49.347 --> 00:00:58.219
I just want to tell y'all thank you, because it's people like you that come on here and pray with me and pray for the lost.

00:00:58.220 --> 00:01:01.577
You're clicking the like button. You're clicking subscribe.

00:01:01.578 --> 00:01:05.996
You're clicking the notification bells. You're commenting something down below.

00:01:05.997 --> 00:01:12.638
Not all of you do, but at least 10% of you almost do. And I just want to say thank you.

00:01:12.639 --> 00:01:17.251
I know some people don't like to comment, but I just want to say those help.

00:01:17.252 --> 00:01:21.869
You don't realize on YouTube, that's how the system works here.

00:01:21.870 --> 00:01:30.445
When they want to see who's interested in your videos, they won't promote you and let new viewers see you unless they see that they're going to make ad revenue.

00:01:30.446 --> 00:01:45.169
Because every time you're watching the video, if they're not making money on me, they go, "Hey, we're not promoting this guy."So if they see that people are interested, they'll let me be in a bigger pool of people through the algorithm.

00:01:45.170 --> 00:02:01.871
So, it's exciting because you coming and staying around and clicking those bells, they go, "Hm, this guy actually has an audience."Even if they don't like what I'm saying, the bottom line is it's about money with the people, and that's the world.

00:02:01.873 --> 00:02:06.772
If it's not making money, they don't promote it. So, I just want to say thank you.

00:02:06.773 --> 00:02:10.836
Thank you from the bottom of our hearts. We want to say thank you.

00:02:10.837 --> 00:02:17.737
And I know Jesus says thank you, too, because we're getting people saved.

00:02:17.738 --> 00:02:31.439
1,218. This channel alone, not all the other six. We have South Korea, Japan, China, all of them. And we give all the glory to Jesus.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:37.528
Braden said, "I didn't even count the salvations on those channels, Dad."So, it probably is over 2,000 with all those.

00:02:37.529 --> 00:02:44.162
So, I just wanted to say thank you all. Thank you. It's exciting to be part of the end-time harvest.

00:02:44.163 --> 00:02:54.315
We're the reapers. We're bringing in the lost one soul at a time, but now it's not just one fish at a fishing pole. We're doing it by the net loads.

00:02:54.316 --> 00:03:03.451
And I just went, "Golly, Lord."I remember as a young man praying in those bathrooms as I was cleaning as a janitor, saying, "God, if You can use me, use me.

00:03:03.452 --> 00:03:13.513
If I can do something to help bring in the lost, help me. I'll do it. I'll do whatever it takes."And that's what it's been.

00:03:13.514 --> 00:03:18.579
And that's why I was telling you all to go back to the awe of God, John Bevere's book.

00:03:18.580 --> 00:03:32.513
Some people, because you've been in this so long, you lose that passion, the drive for relationship with Jesus. And it's all about relationship with Jesus.

00:03:32.514 --> 00:03:44.843
If you follow Jesus and you do it with all your heart, and you lean not unto your own understanding, but in all thy ways you acknowledge Him, He said He'd direct your path.

00:03:44.844 --> 00:03:51.993
He said He would. And that's exactly what He's doing for me. I didn't want to come on YouTube, but just think about all these people that got saved.

00:03:51.994 --> 00:03:57.640
And I thought, we would have never known. Who knows? I pray somebody else would have reached them.

00:03:57.641 --> 00:04:04.675
But the people that God assigns you to help, maybe you're the only one that they'll listen to.

00:04:04.677 --> 00:04:12.292
Maybe. Who knows? But at this moment, at this time, God called us for such a time as this.

00:04:12.293 --> 00:04:15.971
And so, we're excited about the video yesterday, the live stream.

00:04:15.972 --> 00:04:31.952
I feel like it was successful with the turnout of people praying against the tsunamis, because the Lord said, "If you pray..."I saw angel armies coming and standing on the western seashore of California, and we didn't have any major damage.

00:04:31.953 --> 00:04:38.774
