00:04:38.775 --> 00:04:42.788
Japan, I don't even think they had any real major damage from the tsunami.

00:04:42.789 --> 00:04:52.579
But for as large as this earthquake was, I believe it should have caused some major damage, but I don't think it did.

00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:58.319
But the Lord told me, He said, "There will be things that you will not stop.

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:03.434
You need to have your boat ready. You need to know what the Spirit of the Lord is telling you.

00:05:03.435 --> 00:05:14.638
For when these things come, great shaking to awaken, you're going to see."And He talked about the earthquake last night that again happened in the water outside of Oregon, by Portland.

00:05:14.639 --> 00:05:29.804
He said, "Pray over this area. Pray over Seattle. Pray over British Columbia, for a major earthquake is about to take place and you must pray."I saw 30,000 people perish during this.

00:05:29.805 --> 00:05:35.839
Now, can we stop that in prayer? I believe we can. There's a lot of people we can pray for so that they'll not be in harm's way.

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:43.996
I saw just in British Columbia alone, 30,000 people die during that earthquake with buildings falling on them and stuff.

00:05:43.997 --> 00:05:53.089
It was bad, with the tsunamis and all the things. This is what the Lord is warning us about. The other part that the Lord warned us about last night...

00:05:53.090 --> 00:05:58.512
If you remember, He told us, He said, "Brandon, I want you to go over that there'll be many people starting to go home.

00:05:58.513 --> 00:06:09.758
For judgment begins in the house of the Lord first."And it's not just about the preacher behind the stage that is messing around on his wife or husband or whatever is going on.

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:15.637
It's about the whole body, for He said the seed time and harvest is accelerating.

00:06:15.638 --> 00:06:19.117
This is what we talked about. He said seed time and harvest is accelerating.

00:06:19.118 --> 00:06:39.038
Brandon, what He warned me, He said, "What you sow, you're going to reap."As we see the time frame and the acceleration of things happen, as the time frame is becoming shorter and shorter, as the days of Noah, so will it be when the Son of Man returns.

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:51.599
As we see the ark door closing, you can barely see it, but you know that we're on the verge of something huge.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:07:01.088
The raindrops are just starting to hit our foreheads. I know it's not going to rain again this time and we're not going to have a major flood.

00:07:01.089 --> 00:07:09.516
He said, "I won't judge you by water again, but it will be by fire."A major fire is going to judge the earth next time.

00:07:09.517 --> 00:07:17.691
Right? Because that's what the Bible tells us. But we are in that day, as the days of Noah. We're in it right now.

00:07:17.692 --> 00:07:25.503
And there are many of you that are living a compromising lifestyle, and you're living in sin, and you've been a believer your whole life.

00:07:25.504 --> 00:07:29.335
You feel like it's okay. "You know what? I'm just a little lukewarm.

00:07:29.336 --> 00:07:40.460
It's all right."But the more you allow sin in, the sin will keep you longer than you want to stay, and make you pay more than you want to pay.

00:07:40.461 --> 00:07:44.893
I remember this lady named Annette used to tell me that all the time. "You better not be sinning, boy.

00:07:44.894 --> 00:07:49.194
It'll make you pay more than you want to pay and make you stay more than you want to stay."She'd always tell me that.

00:07:49.195 --> 00:07:56.878
I forget the rest of it, but I remember it made me not want to pay more. I don't want to pay nobody nothing.

00:07:56.879 --> 00:08:06.239
I told God, "Okay, God, I don't want to pay the devil nothing."That's what I was saying. The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:18.038
So, what I'm trying to tell you all is, as the Lord keeps warning me to tell y'all, Lot didn't know when a major event was about to happen. It took Abraham interceding for him to send the angels.

00:08:18.039 --> 00:08:25.493
If you're in Sodom and Gomorrah, if you're in a place of compromise and you're not hearing God for yourself, Lot didn't hear God for himself.

00:08:25.494 --> 00:08:31.196
He had to have an intercessor pray for him. And that's what this channel's here for.

00:08:31.197 --> 00:08:39.151
You're here not by coincidence, but for a purpose, just like all the people who got born again in the last couple of days.

00:08:39.152 --> 00:08:45.612
